<p>It might still be useful to integrate with though &#8211; either by running pg_basebackup or just using libpq.T he support for nonexclusive backups probably being the main reason. The &#8220;libpq only&#8221; isn&#8217;t really a big feature in an &#8220;OmniPTR envirnonemnt&#8221;, I think, but the nonexclusive backups might be.</p>
<p>I don&#8217;t think it&#8217;s necessarily a high priority though  <img src="http://www.depesz.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" class="wp-smiley" /> </p>
